      "rationale": "Linear elastic isotropic constitutive model appropriate for Ti-6Al-4V pedicle screw (strains below yield in construct stiffness regime). UHMWPE block modeled as linear elastic, consistent with low-strain quasi-static loading. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) between screw and block validated against literature. Model form uncertainty quantified and included in uval. Gradation 3 satisfied."
