      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and Poisson ratio for Ti-6Al-4V sourced from tensile coupon testing (n=5) of same material lot as test constructs. UHMWPE properties from supplier datasheet confirmed against internal testing. Screw geometry from CMM measurements of three representative screws. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (500 runs). Gradation 3 achieved."
