      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span clinically relevant range of loading rates and environmental conditions; at least two load levels tested.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at single quasi-static loading rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717 standard. Only one test condition evaluated; no variation in loading rate or environmental condition (dry, ambient). This limits the ability to characterize model accuracy across the broader COU loading envelope. Achieved Gradation 2 against required Gradation 3; identified as known gap, accepted given medium model risk and corroborating analytical evidence."
    },
